kafka doesn't needs any installation just doenload extract cd into wxtracted folder and start working...

kafka installation doc -- https://kafka.apache.org/quickstart

kafka has the zookeper inside it just start the zookeeper as well as kafka with the following commands.

# Start the ZooKeeper service
$ bin/zookeeper-server-start.sh config/zookeeper.properties

# Start the Kafka broker service
$ bin/kafka-server-start.sh config/server.properties

# create the topics
$ bin/kafka-topics.sh --create --topic quickstart-events --bootstrap-server localhost:9092

# list the topic
bin/kafka-topics.sh --list --bootstrap-server localhost:9092

start the producer with specific topic to produce events.
bin/kafka-console-producer.sh --topic quickstart-events --bootstrap-server localhost:9092

here the specific topic will be subscribed.
bin/kafka-console-consumer.sh --topic quickstart-events --bootstrap-server localhost:9092 --from-beginning

